metadata.name: Cosa Monstra #1
metadata.description: COSA MONSTRA is a collection of 10,000 unique NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain by GABOR CSUPO, co-creator of Rugrats, Aaahh!!! Real Monsters, The Wild Thornberrys, Rocket Powerand many more childhood classics. Your COSA MONSTRA doubles as an Inkhead Studios Membership Pass with perks, utility and benefits. Owners of COSA MONSTRA have IP & commercial rights with their characters.
